article.linkText: Osunniyi leads St. Bonaventure past Akron 81-74
article.story: CLEVELAND -- — Osun Osunniyi had a career-high 25 points as Saint Bonaventure topped Akron 81-74 on Tuesday. Dominick Welch had 18 points for Saint Bonaventure (1-0). Kyle Lofton added 17 points. Loren Cristian Jackson had 22 points and seven assists for the Zips (1-1). Camron Reece added 12 points and Jermaine Marshall had nine rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
